---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import screenshotLinux from '../assets/images/screenshot-linux.png';
---

<!-- HowItWorks: 3-step flow -->
<section class="section section-dark how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Three steps between you and knowing exactly how fast your money disappears.</p>

    <div class="steps">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/>
            <polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Install</h3>
        <p>One command. No config. Faster than reading your next API bill.</p>
        <code>curl -sL ... | bash</code>
      </div>

      <!-- Arrow -->
      <div class="step-arrow" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="48" height="24" viewBox="0 0 48 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M4 12h36M36 6l6 6-6 6"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Tray icon appears</h3>
        <p>A tiny purple chip appears in your tray. Your new financial anxiety companion.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Arrow -->
      <div class="step-arrow" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="48" height="24" viewBox="0 0 48 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M4 12h36M36 6l6 6-6 6"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-visual">
          <Image src={screenshotLinux} alt="claude-usage tooltip showing progress bars" loading="lazy" format="webp" quality={85} data-lightbox />
        </div>
        <h3>Hover to monitor</h3>
        <p>Hover to see exactly how much Claude is eating. Progress bars, countdowns, regret.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
  }

  .steps {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .step {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .step:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow);
  }

  .step-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg-deep);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(176, 112, 224, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .step-visual {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 220px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step-visual:hover {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .step-visual img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .step h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .step code {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    background: var(--bg-input);
    color: var(--accent);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', Consolas, monospace;
  }

  .step-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--accent-dim);
    opacity: 0.5;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .steps {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .step-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      margin: -0.5rem 0;
    }

    .step {
      max-width: 400px;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>